Detailed Description

This structure contains configuration parameters for each proxy thread.

Field Documentation

uint32_t CSL_ProxyThreadCfg::elSz

Initial queue access mode (see CSL_ProxyQueueAccessMode). Can be overridden by CSL_proxySetQueueAccessMode or CSL_proxySetQueueParms functions

uint32_t CSL_ProxyThreadCfg::errEvtNum

Queue number in the target to use for the proxy thread

uint32_t CSL_ProxyThreadCfg::queueNum

Queue (ring) element size in bytes (4,8,16,32,64,128,256,512)
